				<a href='breaking-news_newtown_new-haven-register-6/index.html'><img width="150" height="150" src="../../../../content/uploads/2013/02/0120_nhr_001-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Outside the fire station where families gather for information about loved ones involved in Sandy Hook Elementary  School shooting in Newtown, CT on December 14, 2012. (Melanie Stengel/ New Haven Register)" /></a>
